<A NAME="chap:polygon_ref"></A><h1>2D Polygons<BR>
<I>Reference&nbsp;Manual</I></h1>

 
<p class="subtitle">Geert-Jan Giezeman  and Wieger Wesselink</p>
<P>

<H3>Assertions</H3>
   
     
     
<A NAME="Index_anchor_1129"></A> 

   

   
     
     
<A NAME="Index_anchor_1130"></A> 

   

The assertion flags for the polygons and polygon operations use 
<I>POLYGON</I> in their names (<I>e.g.</I>, <I>CGAL_POLYGON_NO_ASSERTIONS</I>).
<P>

